Jurgen Klopp announced on Wednesday he will be leaving Borussia Dortmund at the end of the season after seven successful years at the Bundesliga club .
And there will undoubtedly be leading European clubs interested in securing his services , including the Premier League champions .
Manuel Pellegrini could be on his way out at Manchester City .
Klopp won the Bundesliga title twice during his seven years as Dortmund .